# Client Backend Provisioning System

## Objective
Implement a robust provisioning system bound to client backends, allowing clients to provision various instances such as Frappe and Superset within allowed limits. The system orchestrates the creation of these deployments via a dynamic worker queue (`conveyorbelt`), ensuring reliability, auto-scaling, and controlled resource allocation. Real-time setup logs are streamed to clients using `grouplogs`.

